# wocu
Simple cli worldcup score and fixture script.

WoCu is a simple command line script that displays all the scores of past matches and future fixture in a list.

Features - 
It connects up to an internet server to retrieve matches.json file and parses it to display all the matches. 

commands - 
-today -- Displays all the scores/fixtures for today.

It is configured to show the match times in Melbourne, Australia. There is a time conversion function that can 
be configured.